photos from the Roxy in LA on 3/26.  this was a very special homecoming show and we had the chance to invite Linus of Hollywood (who produced and played on Modern Tragedy) and Roger Joseph Manning Jr (who’s played on The Adult Storybook, Bernie, Galaxy Crisis, Love is Calling Me, who I’ve always been inspired by and look up to) join us on stage.  one of my favorites of the tour! (this was our 6th show so I think at this point we played a tighter show too.  but I’ve enjoyed all of them in different ways… )
thanks to @pallooooooon for the awesome photos!!
